<p>[^case] Bertrand Meyer pointed out that OO is <em>case</em> on <em>type</em>)</p>

<ul>
  <li>case on state ==&gt; State Machine (control flow)</li>
  <li>inheritance ==&gt; data</li>
  <li>composition ==&gt; control flow</li>
  <li>override ==&gt; data</li>
  <li>delegation ==&gt; control flow</li>
</ul>

